article_id:2566,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1635487200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The Platinum Showcase and the Scratch-A-Thon Summon that will be live at the same time do not include the limited-time featured adventurers or featured dragon added in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added limited-time featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Halloween Laxi (light/rapid-fire manacaster)</div><div>5★ Halloween Sylas (shadow/bow)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured dragon:</div><div>5★ Gala Chronos Nyx (light)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1635487200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1636005599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
