			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>dispels one buff from each of them, and inflicts<br>flashburn.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 99 × 12 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 4,480<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 7,481<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>・Flashburn<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br></div></dd><dt
