			<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>grants the user a defense amp, and partially<br>fills the clockwork gauge. This skill will deal<br>extra damage and fill more of the clockwork<br>gauge based on the combo count.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 524 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,450<br>Amps:<br>・Defense Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br>Damage Modifier (Based on Combo Count):<br>・25 hit(s) = +10%<br>・50 hit(s) = +20%<br>・75 hit(s) = +30%<br>・100 hit(s) = +40%<br>Gauge Energy Gained (Based on Combo Count):<br>・0 hit(s) = 30%<br>・25 hit(s) = 45%<br>・50 hit(s) = 60%<br>・75 hit(s) = 75%<br>・100 hit(s) = 100%</div></dd></dl></div>
