<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3d35acdfe7f5a710f73a893dfb248ca82.png"></span><span>Clockwork Creature II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user a clockwork gauge that is<br>completely filled at the start of quests.<br><br>When the clockwork gauge is completely filled,<br>it will gradually deplete during force strikes,<br>but will grant the user the following effects until<br>it is completely depleted:<br><br>・Damage dealt by force strikes is increased<br>by 10%.<br>・The rate that force strikes decrease the<br>mode gauge is sped up.<br>・Force strike attack rate is increased by 12%.<br>・Movement speed during force strikes is<br>increased.<br><br>After the clockwork gauge is depleted, it will<br>gradually fill automatically, and the user will not<br>be able to use force strikes until it is filled.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/4a8ec2b478ec8ef017bb1a6ed32684f72.png"></span><span>Curse Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to curses by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/14792abf67fb05b76ddc3021564efff22.png"></span><span>Flashburn Frenzy II</span></dt><dd><div>Extends the window between hitting an enemy<br>and the combo counter resetting by 0.5 seconds.<br><br>Also, increases the user's chances of inflicting<br>flashburn by 25% for every 15-hit combo (up to<br>three times per combo), and grants the user a<br>stack of the "Flashburn Trickster" effect each<br>time they inflict flashburn (up to three times per<br>combo). Flashburn Trickster increases damage<br>to flashburned enemies by 7%. These buffs are<br>removed when the combo counter resets.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>
