			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies in a line,<br>inflicts poison, and dispels one buff<br>from each target.<br><br>If this skill is used while the user has a Combo<br>Sample, a Strike Sample, and a Dash Sample,<br>all three effects will be consumed, and the user<br>will carry out an additional attack that deals<br>damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>dispels one buff from each of them, and inflicts<br>shadowblight.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 1,864 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,520<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>・Poison<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 58.2<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Damage: 1,864 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 171 × 6 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,520<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 13,255<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>・Poison<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 58.2<br>・Shadowblight<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41</div></dd><dt
				>
