			</dt>
			<dd><div>Applies one of the following at random to<br>each member of the entire team:<br><br>・Maximum HP is increased.<br>・Light resistance is increased.<br>・Damage taken is reduced.<br><br>Also, occasionally grants all of the above<br>bonuses at the same time and removes<br>all afflictions.<br><br>If this skill is used while the user has a<br>Combo Sample, a Strike Sample, and a<br>Dash Sample, it grants all of the above<br>bonuses and removes all afflictions,<br>but consumes all three effects.</div><div class="skill-detail">Skill Energy Required: 6,000<br>Special Effects:<br>・HP +15%<br>・10% Damage Reduction<br>　　Lasts 20 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br>・Light Res +20%<br>　　Lasts 10 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br>・Affliction Recovery (All Afflictions)</div></dd></dl></div>
